  "description": "## T-0980 [ ] P0: Провести финальный контроль публичного API 0.1-preview\n\n- Создана: 2026-07-05T12:09:05+03:00\n- Состояние: open\n- Приоритет: P0\n- Execution class: `final-gate`\n- Scheduling tier: `final-gate`\n- Agent action: `verify-only-unless-gate-tooling-evidence-is-missing`\n- Forbidden: `fixing-leaf-class-implementation-or-subsystem-backend-inside-this-task`\n- Output: `data/quality/public-api-010-gate-report.md`; `data/quality/public-api-010-gate-report.json`\n- Зависимости: T-0226, T-0227, T-0241, T-0242, T-0243, T-0244, T-0245, T-0246, T-0247, T-0248, T-0249, T-0250, T-0251, T-0252, T-0253, T-0690, T-0691, T-0692, T-0693, T-0694, T-0695, T-0696, T-0697, T-0698, T-0699, T-0700, T-0701, T-0702, T-0703, T-0704, T-0705, T-0706, T-0707, T-0964, T-0972, T-0973, T-0974, T-0975, T-0976, T-0977, T-0978, T-0979, T-0254, T-0255, T-0256, T-0257, T-0258, T-0259, T-0260, T-0261, T-0262, T-0263, T-0264, T-0265, T-0266, T-0267, T-0268, T-0269, T-0270, T-0271, T-0272, T-0273, T-0274, T-0275, T-0276, T-0277, T-0278, T-0279, T-0280, T-0281, T-0282, T-0283, T-0284, T-0285, T-0286, T-0287, T-0288, T-0289, T-0290, T-0291, T-0292, T-0293, T-0294, T-0295, T-0296, T-0297, T-0298, T-0299, T-0300, T-0301, T-0302, T-0303, T-0304, T-0305, T-0306, T-0307, T-0308, T-0309, T-0310, T-0311, T-0312, T-0313, T-0314, T-0315, T-0316, T-0317, T-0318, T-0319, T-0320, T-0708, T-0709, T-0710, T-0711, T-0712, T-0713, T-0714, T-0715, T-0716, T-0717, T-0718, T-0719, T-0720, T-0721, T-0722, T-0723, T-0724, T-0725, T-0726, T-0727, T-0728, T-0729, T-0730, T-0731, T-0732, T-0733, T-0734, T-0735, T-0321, T-0322, T-0323, T-0324, T-0325, T-0326, T-0327, T-0328, T-0329, T-0330, T-0331, T-0332, T-0333, T-0334, T-0335, T-0736, T-0737, T-0738, T-0739, T-0740, T-0741, T-0742, T-0743, T-0744, T-0745, T-0746, T-0747, T-0748, T-0749, T-0750, T-0751, T-0752, T-0753, T-0754, T-0755, T-0756, T-0757, T-0758, T-0759, T-0760, T-0761, T-0762, T-0763, T-0764, T-0765, T-0965, T-0966, T-0967, T-0968, T