      "kind": "Legacy",
      "payload": {
        "sourceKind": "AgentSummary",
        "text": "Для финального контроля `T-0980` зафиксирован built-in/Variant profile batch: core Variant types approved; `Array`/`Dictionary` approved as `Electron2D.Collections.Array`/`Dictionary` with global `Electron2D.Array`/`Dictionary` unsupported; primitives map to C# `System.Boolean`/`System.Int64`/`System.Double`/`System.String` while `Electron2D.Bool`/`Int`/`Float`/`String` are unsupported; 2D math approved; `Vector3`/`Vector4` and packed variants approved only as data-only/HLSL/editor-compatible numeric types; `AABB`, `Basis`, `Plane`, `Projection`, `Quaternion` and `Transform3D` unsupported as 3D/spatial math."
      }
    },
    {
      "activityEntryId": "legacy-activity-0007",
